decks.notes: The main concept of this deck revolves around utilizing the control elements provided by the commanders Malcolm and Livio to disrupt and manipulate the opponent's strategy. The deck includes a wide range of control cards such as counterspells, removal spells, and bounce effects to maintain board presence and prevent the opponent from executing their game plan efficiently. By using cards like Jace, the Mind Sculptor and Teferi, Hero of Dominaria, the deck aims to generate card advantage and control the tempo of the game. Additionally, the inclusion of cards like True-Name Nemesis and Stoneforge Mystic offers versatile threats and win conditions to close out the game once control is established.
